# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in the real value.
# After the auth re-arch (2026-04-26), the only env var the PWA reads is the
# Cloudflare Worker origin. Per-tablet device tokens are stored in IndexedDB,
# not in the build environment, and are issued by ASPSI ops via the Worker's
# /admin/ UI.
#
# REQUIRED for production builds. `npm run build` fails fast if
# VITE_F2_PROXY_URL is unset or still the REPLACE_ME placeholder (Issue #45).
# Vitest / dev mode are unaffected.

# Cloudflare Worker origin. No trailing slash.
VITE_F2_PROXY_URL=https://f2-pwa-worker.REPLACE_ME.workers.dev

# Filipino translations gate. Set to "true" once src/i18n/locales/fil.ts contains
# real translated strings AND the Apr 20 spec ships Filipino label fields.
# When unset, the LanguageSwitcher is hidden so testers don't toggle FIL and
# see no visible change (placeholder fil.ts values are identical to English).
# VITE_FIL_READY=true
